<br>
my mom really lightened the load when she was here for the first 3weeks...such a blessing. our 'fun' didnt really start till she left. now the bags are really forming under the eyes.<br>
<br>
think moms got a bit of the baby blues too and worries constantly.  but thats why im happy to be able to be home and support her.<br>
<br>
bb's healthy and happy...when hes got a full belly...<br>
<br>
