<br>
really we arent that bad off. he is colic-ee, and can be fairly easily entertained unless he's really hungry. its mostly the stress caused to mom and baby and then me with some of the difficulties that come with feeding.<br>
<br>
im lucky enough to be able to work from home and so amy has some support, but that also adds extra pressures on me...kinda tough to be a good employee or daddy when you have to do both at once...<br>
